{"tid":1421760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手推，關於昨日天水圍","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T00:16:18.000Z","uid":276955,"like":103,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"0d41f575f20adc2305df051a8c0da8675436bcf1","tid":1421760,"uid":276955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:51:48.000Z","msg":"代post<br />\n好難過好難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剛剛收到姐夫電話，話家姐俾人拉左<br />\n就係昨日天水圍一點幾時候拉左果幾十人入面<br />\n但我家姐係住係天耀 果度係佢樓下<br />\n佢只係經過，用電話紀錄警察的行為<br />\n無叫任何口號無任何裝備無口罩<br />\n佢只係一個街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察無任何拘捕原因就拉左佢扣留左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家聯絡左民陣的律師<br />\n但未知幾時可以出番來<br />\n亦聯絡唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天水圍啲警察特別癲我唔係唔知<br />\n但原來會傷害到咁近<br />\n我真係好難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1歲的BB暫時由姐夫照顧<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156777629628650&amp;id=760008649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156777629628650%26id%3D760008649&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=f2ceb419\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156777629628650&amp;id=760008649</a>"},{"pid":"0dd779494c12138bd4c49da1e274e066ca5ad002","tid":1421760,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:52:52.000Z","msg":"扣留咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係話放左一部份人咩"},{"pid":"8d74c0284db7ed6e1910826a50bcfdedbf52e35f","tid":1421760,"uid":276955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep