 />\n會不會不比擔保<br />\n要去提堂？但可以不用通知家屬？下？<br />\n可不可以大家幫手去連登高登討論下？<br />\n我依家知道佢係新屋嶺扣留中心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SA9MMfj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSA9MMfj.jpg&h=ff858280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qP32jAj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqP32jAj.jpg&h=76e2f83d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72a45544009f3fb389f2d873c9fb068fb2ae7fb1","tid":1421760,"uid":167176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:45:42.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"9141e6ecdfe162f4b0a5a2ec09494658cbad80a9","tid":1421760,"uid":276955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d88a3e6aa04c7065d6d7c2bd771cd2abbbf8fa8a","tid":1421760,"uid":260292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:38:49.000Z","msg":"我係原Post人既朋友，以下為事件的跟進<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n昨晚7點幾的家姐最後的cap圖之後無消息了😫😫😫<br />\n唔比用電話 我地聯絡唔到<br />\n姐夫有同民陣律師聯絡<br />\n但依番說話極度令我不安<br />\n而我根本不知我家姐係被咩罪名被拉上<br />\n會不會不比擔保<br />\n要去提堂？但可以不用通知家屬？下？<br />\n可不可以大家幫手去連登高登討論下？<br />\n我依家知道佢係新屋嶺扣留中心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SA9MMfj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSA9MMfj.jpg&h=ff858280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qP32jAj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqP32jAj.jpg&h=76e2f83d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45b9e38ec6798302b4da751b0237c17bc7e0ae3","tid":1421760,"uid":89549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:47:53.000Z","msg":"捱多陣，夠48小時唔到佢唔放人"},{"pid":"22cc6d658a116e34ab6a3cfa7912a1b9cfd24666","tid":1421760,"uid":276955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GoXZm